{"tid":2169000,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"ITZY Lia「無門牙搞笑照片」被成員們設置為手機背景圖！留真：是我們好幾週的笑容按鈕 XD","createTime":"2020-08-22T07:06:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-22T07:36:57.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c9cb4196361ca3bf7ee18b0404553843eee55abc","tid":2169000,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T07:06:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_747dd8d73d078322e918bbb2803b0020/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-08-22/129461-867868.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_747dd8d73d078322e918bbb2803b0020%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-08-22%2F129461-867868.jpg&h=bb538b60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nITZY日前帶著迷你專輯《Not Shy》回歸，同名主打歌也在各大音源榜取得優異的成績，成員們也出演電台、綜藝節目宣傳新曲。<br />\n<br />\n在《DOLympiad》中進行「ITZY測驗」，問了：「Lia以良好的肺活量聞名，你認為她直笛一口氣能吹多久？」結果，證明她肺活量的竟然是...之前在舞台上，亮片意外掉在她的門牙上想要吹掉它動圖（笑）！<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_5c15c20a9b84cde9e8d6c437363b035b/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-08-22/129461-867863.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_5c15c20a9b84cde9e8d6c437363b035b%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-08-22%2F129461-867863.png&h=60fefae7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n彩領：「那個是我們的手機背景。」Lia：「那個我們孩子們都設置成了手機背景。」留真：「是我們好幾週的笑容按鈕。」這也讓不少網友表示：「真的太可愛了」、「怎麼剛好就在門牙上」、「原來她們也知道這個圖」、「我也笑了好久呢」等等。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_a0ed2fbec8cff3f8e5b0c17781cc8278/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-08-22/129461-867864.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_a0ed2fbec8cff3f8e5b0c17781cc8278%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-08-22%2F129461-867864.png&h=75488443&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nITZY日前公開《Not Shy》的練習室舞蹈版，成員們還直接唱起了歌，才兩天的時間已經突破560萬點擊。不少網友更紛紛表示：「真的好穩啊」、「邊跳舞還不喘氣，好厲害」、「唱跳都可以啊」、「竟然是唱現場的」等，大家都看過了嗎？也期待之後其他的舞蹈版本呢！"},{"pid":"b85051f55901dacf8033e549c49ca6ad7b6af97f","tid":2169000,"uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T07:06:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media1.giphy.com/media/MAXgzlCOAs3joqWq9z/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia1.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FMAXgzlCOAs3joqWq9z%2Fgiphy.gif&h=85d46c6d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"26437967d82210623c0fdfc2ee30959d06865085","tid":2169000,"uid":303133,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T07:08:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bf056d9fd9303473454e949a8b1e924feda58da","tid":2169000,"uid":256952,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T07:08:38.000Z","msg":"Old news"},{"pid":"b71c0e1bbe1a6628d0a6ca21e1a06a2ee129a540","tid":2169000,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0bf056d9fd9303473454e949a8b1e924feda58da","tid":2169000,"uid":256952,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T07:08:38.000Z","msg":"Old news"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T07:13:23.000Z","msg":"is so 唔識串"},{"pid":"76dcae42112e279c95e676755b19b62305621c12","tid":2169000,"uid":132174,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"b85051f55901dacf8033e549c49ca6ad7b6af97f","tid":2169000,"uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T07:06:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media1.giphy.com/media/MAXgzlCOAs3joqWq9z/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia1.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FMAXgzlCOAs3joqWq9z%2Fgiphy.gif&h=85d46c6d&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T07:26:20.000Z","msg":"太可愛了吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d06e07741f72b3c3f02a2f614e3d6b142f28b65","tid":2169000,"uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T07:27:11.000Z","msg":"冇成員用佢腳板底?"},{"pid":"7ed1432a2ada9fe56932d80952b6c12ac455b80d","tid":2169000,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b85051f5590